dc_title_s: Iberian Peninsula 1:250,000: Baza, sheet 73. Series A.M.S. M581
dc_description_s: United States. Army Map Service. North Decimal Degree 38.0000. South Decimal Degree 37.0000. East Decimal Degree -2.0000. West Decimal Degree -3.0000. Alternate title: Baza, Spain. Polyconic projection. With Spanish-English glossary. Relief shown by 100 m. contour interval, gradient tint and spot heights. Standard map series designation: A.M.S. M581. "Compiled from Spain, 1:50,000, Instituto Geografico, 1902-35; Spain, 1:200,000, Cuartel General del Generalisimo, sheets 76, undated; 75, 85, 86, 1939; Spain, 1:200,000, Instituto Geografico, PROVINCIA DE GRANADA, 1936, PROVINCIA DE JAEN, 1935 and PROVINCIA DE MURCIA, 1915; Road Map of Spain and Portugal, 1:400,000, AMS, sheet 50, Third Edition, 1943; Railways of Spain & Portugal 1:1,500,000, GSGS, 1942; Railways of Spain, Portugal and Southern France, 1:1,300,000, Military Railway Service, 1943.".
